<h2>Aside 1.5.1</h2>

<p class="intro">A quick fix on top of 1.5.0.</p>

<h3>Fixed</h3>
<ul>
  <li><b>Settings open properly again.</b> Pressing Command-comma, or the Settings item in the app menu, could open an empty window instead of the real settings. Every way in now lands on the same place.</li>
</ul>

<p>If you're coming from an older version, 1.5.0 added agent access (your coding tools can read your meetings), rebuilt speaker detection, and made recordings end themselves when you hang up.</p>
